      "content": "wait adjust the dose myself?? i dont know if i should do that. i feel like the shakiness is getting a bit worse today and the nausea is making it hard to eat. if i just drink a lot more water and maybe take some extra salt like i read online, will that help stabilize it? i really just want to avoid an ER visit if i can just fix it at home.",
